<div
  x-data="
    tabs('tab', {
    content: {
      'x-alt-transition': {
        enter: ['opacity-0', 'transition ease-out duration-100 delay-100', 'opacity-100'],
        leave: ['opacity-100', 'transition ease-in duration-100 absolute top-0', 'opacity-0'],
    }
    }})
  "
>
  <div
    x-bind="tabBar"
    class="flex flex-auto items-center border-b border-secondary-300 pl-2 dark:border-dark-600"
  >
    <button
      data-tab="tab"
      x-bind="label"
      class="-mb-px -ml-px block overflow-ellipsis whitespace-nowrap rounded-t-md border border-secondary-300 p-2 px-4 dark:border-dark-600"
      class-default="bg-secondary-100 hover:bg-secondary-50 dark:bg-dark-900 dark:text-text-300/80 dark:hover:bg-dark-800"
      class-selected="border-b-transparent bg-white shadow-none hover:bg-white dark:border-dark-600 dark:border-b-transparent dark:bg-dark-800 dark:text-text-300 dark:hover:bg-dark-800"
    >
      tab
    </button>
    <button
      data-tab="tab 2"
      x-bind="label"
      class="-mb-px -ml-px block overflow-ellipsis whitespace-nowrap rounded-t-md border border-secondary-300 p-2 px-4 dark:border-dark-600"
      class-default="bg-secondary-100 hover:bg-secondary-50 dark:bg-dark-900 dark:text-text-300/80 dark:hover:bg-dark-800"
      class-selected="border-b-transparent bg-white shadow-none hover:bg-white dark:border-dark-600 dark:border-b-transparent dark:bg-dark-800 dark:text-text-300 dark:hover:bg-dark-800"
    >
      tab 2
    </button>
    <button
      data-tab="tab 3"
      x-bind="label"
      class="-mb-px -ml-px block overflow-ellipsis whitespace-nowrap rounded-t-md border border-secondary-300 p-2 px-4 dark:border-dark-600"
      class-default="bg-secondary-100 hover:bg-secondary-50 dark:bg-dark-900 dark:text-text-300/80 dark:hover:bg-dark-800"
      class-selected="border-b-transparent bg-white shadow-none hover:bg-white dark:border-dark-600 dark:border-b-transparent dark:bg-dark-800 dark:text-text-300 dark:hover:bg-dark-800"
    >
      tab 3
    </button>
  </div>
  <div class="p-4">
    <div class="relative">
      <div data-tab="tab" x-bind="content" x-cloak>
        Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry. Lorem Ipsum has been the industry's
        standard dummy text ever since the 1500s, when an unknown printer took a galley of type and scrambled it to make
        a type specimen book.
      </div>
      <div data-tab="tab 2" x-bind="content" x-cloak>
        It is a long established fact that a reader will be distracted by the readable content of a page when looking at
        its layout. The point of using Lorem Ipsum is that it has a more-or-less normal distribution of letters, as
        opposed to using 'Content here, content here', making it look like readable English.
      </div>
      <div data-tab="tab 3" x-bind="content" x-cloak>
        Contrary to popular belief, Lorem Ipsum is not simply random text. It has roots in a piece of classical Latin
        literature from 45 BC, making it over 2000 years old.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
